Title: Quantifying Crossword Difficulty: Are Monday Puzzles Harder Than Tuesday?
Slug: crossword-difficulty-quantification
Date: 2016-7-8
Tags: webscraping, python, scipy, stats
Author: David Kaleko
Summary: A college friend of mine and I keep in touch by periodically doing L.A. Times daily crossword puzzles. They are supposed to increase in difficulty throughout the week, but we always seem to struggle more with Monday puzzles than with Tuesday puzzles. It's time to put an end to the mystery; are Monday puzzles harder than Tuesday?
Headline: Let's find out!